ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of LYNDA GAIGNARD of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, until June 28, 2012, or until the day prior to the coming into force of the Balanced Refugee Reform Act, whichever is earlier.
